shift_rota_project/
│
├── app.py                  # Main application setup and initialization.
├── models.py               # All your database table definitions (User, Team, etc.).
├── routes.py               # All your webpage routes (@app.route).
├── scheduler.py            # The core scheduling logic and AI validator.
│
├── .env                    # Your secret keys (DATABASE_URL, SECRET_KEY, GEMINI_API_KEY).
├── requirements.txt        # Lists all the Python packages your project needs.
│
├── static/                 # Folder for CSS, JavaScript, and images (optional).
│   └── css/
│       └── style.css
│
└── templates/              # Folder for all your HTML files.
    ├── home.html
    ├── login.html
    ├── signup.html
    ├── dashboard.html
    ├── designation_add.html
    ├── designation_manage.html
    ├── employee_add.html
    ├── employee_manage.html
    ├── team_add.html
    ├── team_manage.html
    ├── team_dashboard.html
    └── generate_schedule.html